Config::INI::Access - Syntactic sugar for accessing data from .ini-files

/*
	Description
*/

Config::INI::Access allows to access configuration data stored in Windows-formatted 
.ini-files with arrows rather than hash braces.

/*
	Installation
*/

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

